reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on November 27, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 5.0 out of 5 stars Perfect for the headrest of my Ford Bronco Sport - I love the bling!
reviews.reviewText: I bought these hooks because I wanted hooks that could hold my Michael Kors backpack purse. The purse has thin handles, so I needed a thinner hook to just put my purse on. I love it, too, because they are long, and I can just reach behind the passenger seat and put my purse and remove it easily. This hook holds it perfectly. It's sturdy as well. I originally bought thicker hooks, but they were too wide for a thin purse handle, and I didn't want to damage my handbag. I love the bling at the bottom since my car has bling all over!

reviews.reviewDate: Reviewed in the United States on September 20, 2023
reviews.reviewTitle: 3.0 out of 5 stars Works great but tears up stitching on your purse handles
reviews.reviewText: These purse hangers are cute and easily fit around the headrests in both my husband's and my cars. However, overtime, as I would pull my purse up off them, the bling on the end caused the stitching on my (expensive) purse to fray and tear apart. These also had a way of spinning around or getting caught as I was pulling my purse off them, causing them to fall off. This could just be my user error as my husband jokes I am a bull in a china shop.
Bought these for my new car so i wouldn't have to put my purse on the floor or on someone's lap. Works like a charm.

I bought these hooks because I saw them in a video and thought they would be super handy in my car. I never use them because the straps of my purses and my grocery bags always get stuck and pull the hook up out of place. You need to fiddle with it in order to take it off. Additionally, in the advent of an accident, the passengers in the backseat could get these hooks jabbed into their face/neck, which is very unsafe. Think before you buy!

reviews.reviewTitle: Beautiful and does what you need them to do :)
reviews.reviewText: Hi There!We love them! I think they are beautiful and wish that I had bought a set for my car too. They were a special gift for my mother, she is very happy. She wished that it was a set of 4. She hangs her grocery bags and her purse on them with no problem. Thank you!
These hooks worked perfectly to hang my water bottle. Strong enough that when the dog leash got hooked by accident it didn't break.
These are pretty and exactly as described. The only thing I would change is to add a little rubber grip so they don't swing around so easily. Handy though and I like them a lot.
